# Hooks, Lib, and Types Directories

## [src/hooks](mdc:web/src/hooks)

Contains custom React hooks for state management and logic reuse. Example: [use-cart.tsx](mdc:web/src/hooks/use-cart.tsx) manages cart state.

## [src/lib](mdc:web/src/lib)

Shared infrastructure and integrations (not feature-specific safe actions). For **actions vs lib** placement, see [actions-vs-lib.mdc](mdc:web/.cursor/rules/actions-vs-lib.mdc).

Utility libraries and integrations:

- [utils.ts](mdc:web/src/lib/utils.ts): General utility functions.
- [server-request.ts](mdc:web/src/lib/server-request.ts): Request URL, search params, and client IP helpers (import from actions via [server-util.ts](mdc:web/src/actions/server-util.ts) when a `"use server"` barrel is required).
- [payment/stripe](mdc:web/src/lib/payment/stripe): Stripe integration (`config`, webhooks, `stripe-money`).
- [payment/paypal](mdc:web/src/lib/payment/paypal): PayPal Orders API helpers (`index` barrel).
- [payment/linePay](mdc:web/src/lib/payment/linePay): LINE Pay integration (legacy camelCase path).
- [auth](mdc:web/src/lib/auth): Authentication helpers.
- [businessHours](mdc:web/src/lib/businessHours): Business hours logic (legacy camelCase path).
- [useTwZipCode2](mdc:web/src/lib/useTwZipCode2): Taiwanese zip code utilities (legacy camelCase path; `data/zip-code.ts`).

## [src/utils](mdc:web/src/utils)

**Generic-only** helpers at **`utils/` root** (no `utils/{domain}/` subfolders). Domain-specific helpers live under **`lib/{domain}/`**. See [file-organization.mdc](mdc:web/.cursor/rules/file-organization.mdc) and [actions-vs-lib.mdc](mdc:web/.cursor/rules/actions-vs-lib.mdc).

- [actions/safe-action.ts](mdc:web/src/utils/actions/safe-action.ts): next-safe-action clients (`storeActionClient`, `adminActionClient`, …).
- [datetime-utils.ts](mdc:web/src/utils/datetime-utils.ts): Epoch BigInt and timezone helpers.
- [is-admin.ts](mdc:web/src/utils/is-admin.ts): Admin session role check.

Domain kernels (e.g. reservation, waitlist, service-staff, image) live under [lib/](mdc:web/src/lib) — e.g. [reservation/](mdc:web/src/lib/reservation), [waitlist/](mdc:web/src/lib/waitlist).

## [src/types](mdc:web/src/types)

Shared TypeScript type definitions for the app. Example: [enum.ts](mdc:web/src/types/enum.ts) contains enums used throughout the codebase.
